    "The original value 2.29 of NE under Val Unseen in HAMT is a typo, which is actually 3.62 and confirmed by one of HAMT's authors.",
    "Note that although the concurrent work ScaleVLN [53] outperforms previous works as well as CONSOLE, it leverages significantly larger data resources and therefore a direct comparison would not be fair.",
